# game/Welcome Party.rpy:57

translate chinese_simplified begin_9c09637d:

    # "This letter is from my hometown, \nMinasato Village."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: オープニング.ks
    "[fn]的少年时代在一个名叫水乡村的乡下村镇度过，信正是从那儿寄来的。"
# game/Welcome Party.rpy:58

translate chinese_simplified begin_f3455657:

    # "Various things started to surface in my mind.{p}That endless blue sky, \nand under it the vast countryside."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: オープニング.ks
    "许多往事在[fn]的脑海中浮现出来。{p}无边无际的天空，一望无际的宽广蔚蓝。{p}天空之下，是美不胜收的田园风景。"
# game/Welcome Party.rpy:59

translate chinese_simplified begin_91d2a4fe:

    # "The sounds of the insects, \nand the murmuring of the streams."
    # [旧版翻译] 来源: オープニング.ks
